      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this fantastic find! This car is in good condition and has been well-maintained, offering a smooth and reliable driving experience. It\u2019s a solid, dependable vehicle that looks great and is ready for many more miles on the road. Come see for yourself why this is such a great value!",
