    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for utility over perfection. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, a small dent on the rear passenger door, and some fading in the clear coat on the roof. Inside, the upholstery shows some staining and wear on the driver's seat bolster, though all electronics remain functional. Mechanically, it runs and drives well, though it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that has plenty of life left for its next owner.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-maintained. The exterior paint still holds a great shine, though there are some minor rock chips on the front bumper and a small, shallow scratch near the rear wheel well. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of odors, with only light wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a consistent service history, making it a reliable and attractive option for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
